# Phase 1

PHASE 1 — PARSE A SINGLE RESOURCE

Goal:

Read a .api file and display its contents.

Support only:

resource Product {
name string
}

No lexer.

No AST.

No compiler.

Regex parsing is acceptable.

Command:

apiforge parse examples/product.api

Expected output:

{
"resource": "Product",
"fields": [
{
"name": "name",
"type": "string"
}
]
}

At the end provide:

* Files created
* Files modified
* Commands to run
* Expected output
* Manual test procedure

Update documentation.

Do not start Phase 2.

